nodes.text: The Zeitooine mission was a Jedi mission to the Inner Rim planet Zeitooine during the High Republic Era. Jedi Knight Dez Rydan participated in the mission, but eventually the strain led him to privately fear he was in danger of giving in to his anger. This led him to request a transfer from Zeitooine to the new space station Starlight Beacon.
